.SS Dictionary
.TP
.B ,d
Look up word under cursor in dictionary (dict.org), shown in a floating window. Press
.B q
or
.B Esc
to close.
.SS Code Completion (nvim-cmp)
.TP
.B C-n
Select next completion item
.TP
.B C-p
Select previous completion item
.TP
.B Tab
Expand or jump to next snippet placeholder (LuaSnip)
.TP
.B S-Tab
Jump to previous snippet placeholder (LuaSnip)
.TP
.B CR
